T1  - THE IMPACT OF LOCAL FISCAL AND MIGRATION POLICIES ON HUMAN CAPITAL ACCUMULATION AND INEQUALITY IN CHINA
AU  - Sieg, Holger
AU  - Yoon, Chamna
AU  - Zhang, Jipeng
Y1  - 2023/02/01
PY  - 2023
DA  - 2023/02/01
DO  - https://doi.org/10.1111/iere.12597
